maps/forest/caves/path-11-to-12.json/ent.orig: Spheromancer Lea! Is something the matter?
That's quite the impressive waterfall, isn't it?
maps/forest/caves/path-11-to-12.json/ent.text: Это довольно впечатляющий водопад, не так ли?

maps/forest/caves/path-11-to-12.json/ent.orig: Lea? Did you see something you remember?
Well then, we should have a closer look around here.
maps/forest/caves/path-11-to-12.json/ent.text: Ну, тогда мы должны здесь получше осмотреться.

maps/forest/caves/path-11-to-12.json/ent.orig: But... make sure to explore the place by yourself.
maps/forest/caves/path-11-to-12.json/ent.text: Но... убедись в том, что исследуешь это место одна.
